event_title: One Foot Out. Expeditions and Diasporas
event_text: The 2016-17 programme of exhibitions at Espai 13 presents artistic works from the periphery of the usual circuits of contemporary art in Barcelona.
event_link: about  "One Foot Out. Expeditions and Diasporas"

event_text: Lluís Maria Riera, an amateur photographer closely associated with the Fundació Joan Miró and the Galeria Joan Prats, was a friend of Miró, Tàpies and Brossa, as well as other artists.
